title: Red Bull Phenom: Alec Majerus
description:
Recently, Volcom's Wild In The Parks tour was approached by Red Bull to select one of its 15-19 year-old competitors to skate in the Red Bull Phenom contest at the 2013 X Games in Los Angeles. Coming straight off a winning effort at 3rd Lair Skatepark Sunday 21, 2013, Alec Majeras has been selected as our tour representative. Good luck to Alec as he represents all of our WITP skaters in LA at the Red Bull Phenom.

Alec's Info:

Birth Date: 5/31/1995 

Place of Birth: Rochester, MN 

Currently Living: Rochester, MN 

Stance: Goofy
